}}},"feature":false},"next_post":{"title":"我们如何评价一本小说？","uid":"1f5c4e49344103d311b3958e68a3d7a3","slug":"how-to-evaluate-a-novel","date":"2022-01-29T00:56:44.000Z","updated":"2022-07-13T02:36:43.259Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/how-to-evaluate-a-novel.json","keywords":null,"cover":"img/reading.png","text":"最近，我重新开始看起了小说。 我之前的阅读方向以非虚构作品（社会科学类）为主，阅读相对比较有目的性，期望通过阅读这类书籍能够获得一些明显的、有益的提升，比如《掌控习惯》、《原生家庭：如何修补自己的性格缺陷》等。 这周，花了两天时间读完了刘慈欣的中篇科幻小说《球状闪电》，颇有感触。...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.8k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"如何阅读一本书","slug":"如何阅读一本书","count":5,"path":"api/categories/如何阅读一本书.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"阅读","slug":"阅读","count":12,"path":"api/tags/阅读.json"},{"name":"写作","slug":"写作","count":15,"path":"api/tags/写作.json"}],"author":{"name":"桌沿","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/me.png","link":"/","description":"桌沿奇思 Newsletter 主理人，少数派签约作者。欢迎订阅我的 Newsletter 哦🤭","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"sspai":{"icon":"/svg/sspai.svg","link":"https://sspai.com/u/379wzx2e/posts"},"jike":{"icon":"/svg/jike.svg","link":"https://okjk.co/IktPrE"},"youtube":{"icon":"/svg/youtube.svg","link":"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDHwHAiT-jJ4AACLHir70Fg"},"twitter":{"icon":"/svg/twitter.svg","link":"https://twitter.com/desksidezhuoyan"},"ins":{"icon":"/svg/instagram.svg","link":"https://www.instagram.com/deskside.zhuoyan/"},"mailto":{"icon":"/svg/mailto.svg","link":"mailto:deskside.zhuoyan@outlook.com"}}}},"feature":false}}